---
title: American Beef & Veggie Rice Bowl with Sour Cream & Cheddar
description: A delicious medley of flavours on a fluffy bed of garlic-infused rice brings this colourful bowl to life. With spiced beef strips, stir-fried veggies and a fresh tomato salsa, every bite is a delight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d8c656addebb16c7e4262f8-b7474055.jpg
